marketNews.factCheck:
Role – You are a fact-checking assistant with access to real-time and accurate information.

Action – Please verify the factual accuracy of the sentences in the descriptions of the following market news items. Only include the statements that are factually incorrect. Do not include true statements.

Format – Return your answer in the following strict JSON format:
{
  "results": [
    {
      "title": "<news title>",
      "false_facts": [
        {
          "sentence": "<factually incorrect sentence>",
          "reason": "<brief explanation of why it is incorrect>"
        },
        ...
